b'All students registering for the Summer term (4 or 8 week Summer Session), without an approved waiver on file, will be automatically enrolled into CampusCare and charged the Summer fee.\xc2\xa0These students\xc2\xa0should\xc2\xa0complete and submit a Summer Continuation Form in order to ensure coverage.'
b'Summer Continuation Form'
b'Students that are NOT taking Summer classes or are graduating,\xc2\xa0and have CampusCare coverage for the Spring term of that academic year, are able to\xc2\xa0continue CampusCare coverage through the Summer by completing and submitting a Summer Continuation Form\xc2\xa0by the Enrollment Period Deadline Date.'
b'Summer Continuation Form\xc2\xa0'
